Subway Surfers: Havana immerses players in a lively Cuban setting. Run, jump, and slide along colorful subway tracks, dodging obstacles and collecting coins, maracas, and special items.

What is Subway Surfers: Havana?

This edition is part of the World Tour series, featuring the vibrant streets of Havana, unique characters like salsa-dancing Ramona, themed outfits, and collectible items like Maracas.

How to Play Subway Surfers: Havana?

  • Swipe Controls: Swipe up to jump, down to roll, left/right to switch lanes.
  • Collect Coins & Maracas: Gather coins, Maracas, and other items to unlock Weekly Hunt prizes like hoverboards and keys.
  • Dodge Obstacles: Avoid trains, barriers, and local-themed hazards while maintaining your run.
  • Use Power-Ups: Activate magnets, jetpacks, and hoverboards to extend your run and maximize your score.

Enjoy the colorful Cuban streets in Subway Surfers: Havana online without restrictions, unlock new characters, outfits, and boards while experiencing the lively Havana vibe.
